<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Churuata Registration</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Dear ${label.name.title},</h1>
    <p>Thank you so much for registering your service to <strong>Churuata
        Digital</strong>! We are so happy with all the help we can get to
      support refugees all over the world. </p>
    <p>As you know, people in need need all the support and protection they can
      get, and so I am sure you will agree that we will first try to contact you
      through the contact information you provided, in order to see if your
      support meets our standards of safety and protection. </p>
    <p>By clicking the check-boxes below, you agree to our terms of use and our
      privacy policy. If you complete the registration, you will contacted by
      our staff as soon as possible for an intake. after this you will receive
      an email with a link to confirm the registration process.</p>
    <p>Thank you again for your valuable support!</p>
    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p>${label.team.title}</p>
    <p><br>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
